graph LR
    KServe[KServe Operator<br/>Component]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KServe -->|platform| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.24+<br/>REQUIRED]
    KServe -->|certificates| CertManager[cert-manager 1.9+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional - Serverless Mode)
    KServe -->|autoscaling<br/>serverless mode| Knative[Knative Serving 1.8+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    KServe -->|traffic mgmt<br/>service mesh| Istio[Istio 1.16+<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    KServe -->|creates resources| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - Istio<br/>VirtualService CRD]
    KServe -.->|future API calls| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Model metadata]
    KServe -->|creates services| KnativeInternal[Knative Serving<br/>Knative Service CRD]

    %% Integration Points - Incoming
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management<br/>K8s API| KServe
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|auto deploy<br/>K8s API| KServe

    %% External Services (Storage)
    KServe -->|model storage<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>S3 API| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>AWS S3, MinIO]
    KServe -->|model storage<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>GCS API| GCS[Google Cloud Storage<br/>GCP]

    %% External Services (Infrastructure)
    KServe -->|CRD reconciliation<br/>HTTPS/6443| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    KServe -->|metrics export<br/>HTTP/8080| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Monitoring]

    %% Deployment Mode Dependencies
    subgraph "Serverless Mode (Default)"
        Knative
        Istio
    end

    subgraph "RawDeployment Mode"
        K8sOnly[Kubernetes Only<br/>No Knative/Istio required]
    end

    subgraph "ModelMesh Mode"
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh Controller<br/>Separate installation]
    end

    KServe -.->|deployment mode| K8sOnly
    KServe -.->|deployment mode| ModelMesh

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    subgraph "Model Server Runtimes"
        direction TB
        SKLearn[sklearn-server<br/>Python]
        XGBoost[xgboost-server<br/>Python]
        TensorFlow[tensorflow-serving<br/>C++]
        PyTorch[torchserve<br/>Java]
        Triton[triton-server<br/>NVIDIA]
        HuggingFace[huggingface-server<br/>Python]
    end

    KServe -->|runtime templates| SKLearn
    KServe -->|runtime templates| XGBoost
    KServe -->|runtime templates| TensorFlow
    KServe -->|runtime templates| PyTorch
    KServe -->|runtime templates| Triton
    KServe -->|runtime templates| HuggingFace

